messages.content:
Draft the resolution email for the following dispute. Use the inputs verbatim where they appear in the email; do not invent or paraphrase numbers, IDs, or names.

CUSTOMER
- Name: {{input.customer_name}}
- Tier: {{input.customer_tier}}
- Account flags: {{input.flags}}

DISPUTE
- Invoice number: {{input.invoice_number}}
- Customer's description: "{{input.dispute_description}}"
- Analyst root cause: {{input.root_cause}}
- Recommended resolution: {{input.recommended_resolution}}
- Line items affected: {{input.line_items_summary}}

ADJUSTMENT POSTED
- Adjustment type: {{input.adjustment_type}}
- Adjustment ID: {{input.adjustment_id}}
- Credit amount: ₹{{input.credit_amount}}
- Adjusted invoice balance: ₹{{input.adjusted_invoice_balance}}

SIGN-OFF
- Finance manager: {{input.finance_manager_name}}
- Company: {{input.company_name}}

Return only the JSON object: { "subject": "...", "body": "..." }.
